OL,3,CGovernment pulls Hillsborough Law spy
OL,4,Camendment after backlash
OL,6,FThe Government has pulled an amendment
OL,7,Fto its Hillsborough Law amid concerns
OL,8,Fthat intelligence agencies could use
OL,9,Fit to avoid being bound by the
OL,10,Fproposed duty of candour.
OL,12,FIt also withdrew the legislation from
OL,13,FMonday's parliamentary agenda entirely
OL,14,Fafter initially planning for its
OL,15,Freport stage and third reading to go
OL,16,Fahead and then bring forward
OL,17,Famendments in the Lords.
OL,19,FMinisters are now speaking with
OL,20,Fcampaigners and bereaved families to
OL,21,Ftry to agree on how to move forward.
