OL,6,FThe proposed law ` formally the Public
OL,7,FOffice (Accountability) Bill ` aims to
OL,8,Fforce public officials and contractors
OL,9,Fto tell the truth after disasters.
OL,11,FAmendments tabled last week brought
OL,12,Fspies within the scope of the
OL,13,Flegislation, subject to the approval
OL,14,Fof the head of their service, but
OL,15,Fcampaigners argued this would allow
OL,16,Fthose running the security services to
OL,17,Fdecide whether to disclose information.
