OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "This
OL,7,Flegislation will right the wrongs of
OL,8,Fthe past, changing the balance of
OL,9,Fpower to ensure the state can never
OL,10,Fhide from the people it should serve
OL,11,Fand putting a legal duty on officials
OL,12,Fto respond openly and honestly when
OL,13,Fthings go wrong.
OL,15,F"The Bill will make the police,
OL,16,Fintelligence agencies and the whole of
OL,17,Fgovernment more scrutinised than they
OL,18,Fhave ever been. We must get this right
OL,19,Fto keep the country safe.
