OL,6,FMPs had been due to debate the
OL,7,FHillsborough Law last week but the
OL,8,Fdiscussion was pushed back until
OL,9,FMonday to allow the Government to
OL,10,Fpropose changes that might address
OL,11,Fcampaigners' concerns.
OL,13,FHowever, the amendment put forward
OL,14,Fdrew criticism from campaigners and
OL,15,FLabour figures.
OL,17,FLiverpool West Derby MP Ian Byrne had
OL,18,Fsaid he would not be able to support
OL,19,Fthe legislation with the Government's
OL,20,Famendments included.
