OL,6,FLiverpool City Region mayor Steve
OL,7,FRotheram and Greater Manchester mayor
OL,8,FAndy Burnham said on Saturday that the
OL,9,FGovernment amendment "risks
OL,10,Fundermining the spirit of the
OL,11,Flegislation" and "creates too broad an
OL,12,Fopt-out" for the security services.
OL,14,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy insisted
OL,15,Fearlier on Sunday that security
OL,16,Fservices would not be "exempt" from
OL,17,Fthe duty of candour.
